name: Stress
description: Hi, I'm Art (@artmin) and my daughter asked to create a NFT with one of her cartoons. It was a wakeup call reminding me that kids are people too. Here's her description of this piece: "I've been really stressed lately. I feel like I'm drowning and I'm not sure when I get to catch my breath. I think it's because of remote school, not seeing my friends, and hearing about how so many people are not doing so great. I would like to share this drawing with anyone that feels the same." Lauren - Age 10
